      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Or you take your app and one group Msha's on a stick to gear them up faster. Honestly between Msha's and places like Time and Tacvi it's not hard to gear up new people. Epics on the other hand take alot of time and time away from major targets to a guild become a burden. Often times an epic is a reward for longer term members, as this practice also prevents guild hopping after a quick grandfathering/flag run. Hate to say it, but most guilds repulse at getting new people their epics very quickly because alot of us have fond memories of being in a feeder guild to have a new guy get his epic and then apply to uber guild01 two days later.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
